message:

title: 820-01700-A stuck at 20V 0.05A
message: I cant get it in DFU mode, do I need to have the battery present to enter DFU?

title: 820-01700-A stuck at 20V 0.05A
message:
The board can get into DFU without charger even.
5V through USB-C from AC2 machine is good enough.

Check if you get all AWAKE and SLPS2R voltages.
